<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<style>
  {{ font_faces }}
  {{ base_css }}
  @page { size: A4; margin: 22mm 20mm; }
  .header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; }
  .brandmark { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 9px; }
  .brandmark img { width: 42px; height: 42px; }
  .brandmark .wm { font-family: '{{ tokens.font_display }}'; font-weight: 800;
                   font-size: 13pt; letter-spacing: .02em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .sender { text-align: right; font-family: '{{ tokens.font_mono }}'; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 1.4; }
  .addressee { margin-top: 18px; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4; }
  .date { margin-top: 14px; font-family: '{{ tokens.font_mono }}'; font-size: 9pt; }
  .body { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.55; }
  .body p { margin-bottom: 11px; }
  .finding { border-left: 4px solid {{ tokens.coral }}; padding: 6px 0 6px 12px;
             background: {{ tokens.cream }}; font-weight: 500; }
  .claim { margin-top: 18px; border: {{ tokens.border }}; box-shadow: {{ tokens.shadow }};
           padding: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
  .claim .qr img { width: 92px; height: 92px; }
  .claim .url { font-family: '{{ tokens.font_mono }}'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: 700; }
  .sign { margin-top: 22px; }
  .sign .name { font-family: '{{ tokens.font_display }}'; font-weight: 800; font-size: 13pt; }
  .ps { margin-top: 16px; font-style: italic; }
  .foot { margin-top: 22px; padding-top: 8px; border-top: {{ tokens.border }};
          font-family: '{{ tokens.font_mono }}'; font-size: 8.5pt; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="brandmark">
      <img src="logo.svg" alt="Antek Automation">
      <span class="wm">Antek&nbsp;Automation</span>
    </div>
    <div class="sender">
      {% for line in tokens.address_lines %}{{ line }}<br>{% endfor %}
      {{ tokens.phone }}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="addressee">
    {{ addressee }}<br>
    {{ company.name }}<br>
    {% if delivery_address %}{{ delivery_address }}{% endif %}
  </div>

  <div class="date">{{ date_str }}</div>

  <div class="body">
    <p>Dear {{ salutation }},</p>

    <p class="finding">{{ headline }}</p>

    <p>I run Antek Automation in Andover. I have been checking how {{ company.town }}
       {{ sector_word }} show up when people ask AI tools like ChatGPT for a
       recommendation. That is how a lot of your customers now start looking.</p>

    <p>Roughly 85% of UK SMEs have zero measurable AI visibility. Most have no
       idea, because it does not show up in the places they usually check.</p>

    <p>I put together a short AI Visibility Check report for {{ company.name }}. It
       shows exactly where you appear across ChatGPT, Perplexity and Google's AI
       results, and where a competitor appears instead. It is free and it is
       already prepared. You just need to claim it.</p>

    <div class="claim">
      {% if qr_data_uri %}<div class="qr"><img src="{{ qr_data_uri }}" alt="Claim QR code"></div>{% endif %}
      <div>
        <div>Scan the code, or go to:</div>
        <div class="url">{{ claim_url }}</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sign">
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <div class="name">{{ tokens.operator }}</div>
      <div>{{ tokens.company_name }}</div>
    </div>

    <p class="ps">PS. No catch. The report exists either way. I'd rather you saw it.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="foot">
    {{ tokens.company_name }} · {{ tokens.address_lines|join(', ') }} · {{ tokens.phone }} · {{ tokens.website }}
  </div>
</body>
</html>
